# Banking Transaction PDF to CSV Processor

Convert banking transaction PDFs to CSV format for easy analysis and record-keeping.

## Quick Start

1. Place your banking transaction PDF files in the `input/` directory
2. Run the processing script (to be implemented)
3. Find your CSV files in the `output/` directory

## Directory Structure

```
finance/
├── input/          # Place PDF files here
├── output/         # CSV files generated here
├── scripts/        # Processing scripts
├── CLAUDE.md       # Project context for Claude
├── README.md       # This file
└── .gitignore      # Ignores PDFs and CSVs (sensitive data)
```

## Important Notes

- **Security**: PDF and CSV files are gitignored by default as they may contain sensitive banking information
- Keep your source PDFs in the `input/` directory
- Processed CSV files will be saved to `output/` directory

